---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';

const base = import.meta.env.BASE_URL.replace(/\/$/, '');
---

<Layout
  title="關於嘉義國本學堂 | 開源農業知識平台"
  description="嘉義國本學堂的願景、使命與社群故事。我們致力於將農業課程與在地經驗，轉化為開源、可持續的知識資產。"
>
  <main class="about-page">
    <!-- Hero Section -->
    <section class="hero">
      <div class="container">
        <h1>嘉義國本學堂</h1>
        <p class="tagline">將農業課程與在地經驗，轉化為開源、可持續的知識平台</p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Vision Section -->
    <section class="section vision-section">
      <div class="container">
        <h2>我們的願景</h2>
        <div class="vision-grid">
          <div class="vision-card">
            <div class="icon">📖</div>
            <h3>公開可讀</h3>
            <p>任何人都能免費瀏覽、學習嘉義農業知識，無論背景或經驗。</p>
          </div>
          <div class="vision-card">
            <div class="icon">🔓</div>
            <h3>開源可編修</h3>
            <p>以 Markdown 為主體，方便協作與版本管理，社群力量形塑內容。</p>
          </div>
          <div class="vision-card">
            <div class="icon">🌱</div>
            <h3>可持續成長</h3>
            <p>隨著課程、案例、交流持續擴充，成為活的農業知識庫。</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Origin Story -->
    <section class="section origin-section">
      <div class="container">
        <h2>如何開始</h2>
        <div class="origin-content">
          <p>
            <strong>嘉義國本學堂</strong> 起源於嘉義縣政府農業處的農業課程與田間實驗。
          </p>
          <p>
            多年來，農業課程累積了大量珍貴的實務經驗——從土壤改良、作物栽培、設施管理，到農場經營與市場策略。
            這些知識原本只在課堂上流轉，難以被整體保存與傳承。
          </p>
          <p>
            2025 年，我們決定將這些課程轉化為<strong>開源、可搜尋、可協作</strong>的知識平台。
            讓新農、返鄉青年、學生與農業社群，都能快速找到實用的農業知識。
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Target Audience -->
    <section class="section audience-section">
      <div class="container">
        <h2>這個平台為誰而建</h2>
        <div class="audience-grid">
          <div class="audience-card">
            <span class="emoji">🌾</span>
            <h4>新農與返鄉青年</h4>
            <p>快速掌握農業入門知識，建立第一個農場計畫</p>
          </div>
          <div class="audience-card">
            <span class="emoji">🎓</span>
            <h4>學生與研究者</h4>
            <p>從在地案例與實務經驗中學習農業科學</p>
          </div>
          <div class="audience-card">
            <span class="emoji">🚜</span>
            <h4>農場經營者</h4>
            <p>探索進階技術、經營策略與市場趨勢</p>
          </div>
          <div class="audience-card">
            <span class="emoji">🤝</span>
            <h4>農業社群</h4>
            <p>共同維護、補充、改進知識內容</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Knowledge Structure -->
    <section class="section structure-section">
      <div class="container">
        <h2>知識架構</h2>
        <p class="intro">我們將農業知識分為 10 大主題，涵蓋從入門到進階的完整學習路徑：</p>

        <div class="topics-grid">
          <div class="topic-item">
            <span class="num">1</span>
            <h4><a href={`${base}/agri-basics`}>農業基礎入門</a></h4>
            <p>土壤、水資源、有機農法與入門概念</p>
          </div>
          <div class="topic-item">
            <span class="num">2</span>
            <h4><a href={`${base}/agri-advanced`}>農業進階實務</a></h4>
            <p>栽培進階管理、實作工作坊與經驗整理</p>
          </div>
          <div class="topic-item">
            <span class="num">3</span>
            <h4><a href={`${base}/farm-management`}>農場經營管理</a></h4>
            <p>財務、人力、經營策略與永續發展</p>
          </div>
          <div class="topic-item">
            <span class="num">4</span>
            <h4><a href={`${base}/crop-production`}>作物生產技術</a></h4>
            <p>小番茄、百香果等嘉義特色作物實務</p>
          </div>
          <div class="topic-item">
            <span class="num">5</span>
            <h4><a href={`${base}/facility-farming`}>設施農業</a></h4>
            <p>溫室、環控、滴灌與設施規劃</p>
          </div>
          <div class="topic-item">
            <span class="num">6</span>
            <h4><a href={`${base}/smart-farming`}>智慧農業</a></h4>
            <p>感測器、灌溉自動化、無人機與數據分析</p>
          </div>
          <div class="topic-item">
            <span class="num">7</span>
            <h4><a href={`${base}/agri-marketing`}>農產品銷售</a></h4>
            <p>品牌建立、通路開拓與銷售策略</p>
          </div>
          <div class="topic-item">
            <span class="num">8</span>
            <h4><a href={`${base}/grants-planning`}>計畫撰寫補助</a></h4>
            <p>農業補助申請與提案能力培養</p>
          </div>
          <div class="topic-item">
            <span class="num">9</span>
            <h4><a href={`${base}/field-visits`}>場域交流觀摩</a></h4>
            <p>參訪紀錄、交流會與案例觀摩</p>
          </div>
          <div class="topic-item">
            <span class="num">10</span>
            <h4><a href={`${base}/livestock-health`}>畜牧健康</a></h4>
            <p>家禽家畜管理與健康議題</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- How It Works -->
    <section class="section how-works">
      <div class="container">
        <h2>運作方式</h2>
        <div class="tech-flow">
          <div class="flow-step">
            <div class="step-num">1</div>
            <div class="step-content">
              <h4>Markdown 為真相來源</h4>
              <p>所有內容存放於 <code>knowledge/</code> 目錄，保持版本控制與透明度</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="flow-arrow">→</div>
          <div class="flow-step">
            <div class="step-num">2</div>
            <div class="step-content">
              <h4>自動同步投影層</h4>
              <p>內容經過驗證與清理，同步到網站渲染層</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="flow-arrow">→</div>
          <div class="flow-step">
            <div class="step-num">3</div>
            <div class="step-content">
              <h4>GitHub Pages 靜態部署</h4>
              <p>構建為靜態網站，快速、安全、無需伺服器</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Features -->
    <section class="section features">
      <div class="container">
        <h2>平台特性</h2>
        <div class="features-grid">
          <div class="feature-card">
            <div class="feature-icon">🔍</div>
            <h4>全文搜尋</h4>
            <p>快速找到相關農業主題與概念</p>
          </div>
          <div class="feature-card">
            <div class="feature-icon">🕸️</div>
            <h4>知識圖譜</h4>
            <p>視覺化探索文章之間的關聯與知識網絡</p>
          </div>
          <div class="feature-card">
            <div class="feature-icon">📱</div>
            <h4>開放資料 API</h4>
            <p>開放 JSON API 供第三方應用整合</p>
          </div>
          <div class="feature-card">
            <div class="feature-icon">📰</div>
            <h4>RSS Feed</h4>
            <p>訂閱最新文章更新</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- FAQ -->
    <section class="section faq">
      <div class="container">
        <h2>常見問題</h2>
        <div class="faq-list">
          <div class="faq-item">
            <h4>我可以引用或分享這些內容嗎？</h4>
            <p>
              可以。本平台所有內容採用 <strong>CC BY-SA 4.0</strong> 授權，
              允許自由分享與改編，只需標明出處即可。
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="faq-item">
            <h4>我可以如何貢獻內容？</h4>
            <p>
              歡迎！請參考 <a href={`${base}/contribute`}>貢獻指南</a>，
              或直接 Fork 本專案的 GitHub repo，貢獻新文章或改進現有內容。
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="faq-item">
            <h4>為什麼選擇開源模式？</h4>
            <p>
              農業知識應該被共享與持續改進。開源模式能確保內容透明、可驗證、
              並能吸引農業社群一同維護與演進。
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="faq-item">
            <h4>平台上的內容來自哪裡？</h4>
            <p>
              內容主要來自嘉義縣政府農業處國本學堂課程、農業課程學員的實務經驗、
              以及社群貢獻者的知識分享。
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- CTA -->
    <section class="section cta">
      <div class="container">
        <h2>開始探索</h2>
        <div class="cta-buttons">
          <a href={`${base}/`} class="btn btn-primary">首頁</a>
          <a href={`${base}/agri-basics`} class="btn btn-secondary">農業入門</a>
          <a href={`${base}/graph`} class="btn btn-secondary">知識圖譜</a>
          <a href={`${base}/contribute`} class="btn btn-secondary">加入貢獻</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
</Layout>

<style>
  .about-page {
    background: #fff;
  }

  .container {
    max-width: 900px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 2rem;
  }

  .hero {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1a472a 0%, #2d5a3d 100%);
    color: white;
    padding: 6rem 2rem;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .hero h1 {
    font-size: clamp(2rem, 6vw, 3.5rem);
    margin: 0 0 1rem 0;
    font-weight: 700;
  }

  .tagline {
    font-size: 1.3rem;
    opacity: 0.95;
    max-width: 600px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    line-height: 1.5;
  }

  .section {
    padding: 4rem 2rem;
  }

  .section h2 {
    font-size: 2rem;
    margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
    text-align: center;
    color: #1a1a2e;
  }

  .intro {
    text-align: center;
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    color: #666;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    max-width: 700px;
    margin-left: auto;
    margin-right: auto;
  }

  /* Vision Grid */
  .vision-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));
    gap: 2rem;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .vision-card {
    background: #f9fafb;
    border-radius: 12px;
    padding: 2rem;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .icon {
    font-size: 3rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    display: block;
  }

  .vision-card h3 {
    font-size: 1.3rem;
    margin: 1rem 0;
    color: #1a1a2e;
  }

  .vision-card p {
    color: #666;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  /* Origin Section */
  .origin-content {
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    line-height: 1.8;
    color: #4b5563;
  }

  .origin-content p {
    margin: 1.5rem 0;
  }

  /* Audience Grid */
  .audience-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr));
    gap: 2rem;
  }

  .audience-card {
    background: #fef8f3;
    border-left: 4px solid #d4a574;
    padding: 1.5rem;
    border-radius: 8px;
  }

  .emoji {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    display: block;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .audience-card h4 {
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    margin: 0.5rem 0;
    color: #1a1a2e;
  }

  .audience-card p {
    color: #666;
    margin: 0;
  }

  /* Topics Grid */
  .topics-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
    gap: 1.5rem;
  }

  .topic-item {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 40px 1fr;
    gap: 1rem;
    padding: 1.5rem;
    background: #f9fafb;
    border-radius: 8px;
    border-left: 3px solid #1a472a;
  }

  .num {
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    color: #1a472a;
  }

  .topic-item h4 {
    margin: 0;
    color: #1a1a2e;
  }

  .topic-item h4 a {
    color: inherit;
    text-decoration: none;
  }

  .topic-item h4 a:hover {
    color: #1a472a;
    text-decoration: underline;
  }

  .topic-item p {
    margin: 0.5rem 0 0 0;
    color: #666;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
  }

  /* Tech Flow */
  .tech-flow {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr auto 1fr auto 1fr;
    gap: 1.5rem;
    align-items: center;
    margin: 2rem 0;
  }

  .flow-step {
    background: #f9fafb;
    padding: 2rem;
    border-radius: 12px;
    border-left: 4px solid #1a472a;
  }

  .step-num {
    background: #1a472a;
    color: white;
    width: 40px;
    height: 40px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    font-weight: 700;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .step-content h4 {
    margin: 0.5rem 0;
    color: #1a1a2e;
  }

  .step-content p {
    color: #666;
    margin: 0.5rem 0 0 0;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
  }

  .flow-arrow {
    color: #1a472a;
    font-size: 2rem;
    text-align: center;
  }

  /* Features Grid */
  .features-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(240px, 1fr));
    gap: 2rem;
  }

  .feature-card {
    text-align: center;
  }

  .feature-icon {
    font-size: 3rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .feature-card h4 {
    color: #1a1a2e;
    margin: 0.5rem 0;
  }

  .feature-card p {
    color: #666;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
  }

  /* FAQ */
  .faq-list {
    display: grid;
    gap: 1.5rem;
  }

  .faq-item {
    background: #f9fafb;
    padding: 1.5rem;
    border-radius: 8px;
    border-left: 4px solid #d4a574;
  }

  .faq-item h4 {
    margin: 0 0 0.75rem 0;
    color: #1a1a2e;
  }

  .faq-item p {
    margin: 0;
    color: #4b5563;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .faq-item a {
    color: #1a472a;
    text-decoration: underline;
  }

  /* CTA */
  .cta {
    background: #f9fafb;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .cta h2 {
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .cta-buttons {
    display: flex;
    gap: 1rem;
    justify-content: center;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  .btn {
    display: inline-block;
    padding: 0.75rem 1.5rem;
    border-radius: 8px;
    text-decoration: none;
    font-weight: 600;
    transition: all 0.2s;
    border: none;
    cursor: pointer;
  }

  .btn-primary {
    background: #1a472a;
    color: white;
  }

  .btn-primary:hover {
    background: #0f2e1a;
  }

  .btn-secondary {
    background: white;
    color: #1a472a;
    border: 2px solid #1a472a;
  }

  .btn-secondary:hover {
    background: #1a472a;
    color: white;
  }

  code {
    background: #e5e7eb;
    padding: 0.2em 0.4em;
    border-radius: 4px;
    font-family: monospace;
  }

  @media (max-width: 640px) {
    .section {
      padding: 2.5rem 1rem;
    }

    .section h2 {
      font-size: 1.5rem;
    }

    .tech-flow {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 1rem;
    }

    .flow-arrow {
      display: none;
    }

    .cta-buttons {
      flex-direction: column;
    }

    .btn {
      width: 100%;
      text-align: center;
    }
  }
</style>
